oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: For The Good Old USA - Nora Lou Martin with the Pals of the Golden West performance
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance of For The Good Old USA, written by Myers [unconfirmed], and performed by Nora Lou Martin with the Pals of the Golden West [unconfirmed]. The Pals of the Golden West feature Scotty Harrell (guitar), Art Wenzel (accordion), Larry Shaw (guitar), Roy "Bud" Jackson (clarinet).
